==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: earpiece
<hw>earpiece</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>a device for converting electric
signals into sounds, designed to be held over or inserted into the ear;
<as>as, The common <partof>telephone handset</partof> has a speaker and
an <ex>earpiece</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> earphone, headphone, phone.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

